title: It's The First Show of 2022!
description: Welcome to 2022! Here's what we did to kickstart the New Year! Caught up with some Personal Stories from the holiday, What were our 2021 predictions?, Your funny family game night stories, A new Group Therapy, Weekend X Factor, JoJo Siwa ticket giveaway, can you guess what we each did for New Years?, & More!
